To set up Xvfb for running the plugin in an environment with no GUI:
-Install Xvfb and run
/usr/bin/Xvfb :1 -screen 0 1024x768x24 &
export DISPLAY=:1

To generate xml from MagicDraw from the command line:
-Get script isfpluginexec.sh from MagicDrawCompPlugin directory of Rel1.6-NewSchema branch
-Set environmental variable INSTALLDIR to the root install directory of MagicDraw
-Set environmental variable BUILD_ROOT to the root of the isf git directory
-Run the command
./isfpluginexec.sh -project_name <project> -verbose

